    <title>SpringMvc总结</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/11/30/test3/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/11/30/test3/</id>
    <published>2020-11-30T06:44:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-11-30T08:03:03.139Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Begin"><a href="#Begin" class="headerlink" title="Begin"></a>Begin</h1><p>   这几天对SpringMvc进行了一些学习，以下归纳了一些知识点和个人对该框架的一些理解，结合了一些网上的资料，做出了以下总结，仅供参考。</p><p>   首先，我们要了解JavaEE的层次结构，其层次结构分为四个，分别为应用层、Web层、业务层以及持久层。其中，Spring作用于业务层，SpringMVC作用与Web层，MyBatis以及HiBernate作用于持久层。</p><h1 id="SpringMVC的基本知识"><a href="#SpringMVC的基本知识" class="headerlink" title="SpringMVC的基本知识"></a>SpringMVC的基本知识</h1><p>​    Model:封装了应用的数据，一般会与数据之间形成POJO</p><p>​    View:负责呈现数据，一般由HTML实现</p><p>​    Controller:负责处理请求，并将数据传递到View</p><p> <strong>Spring MVC围绕DispatcherServlet(前端控制器)为中心展开</strong>，DispatcherServlet(前端控制器)是Spring MVC的中枢，和MVC的思想一样，它负责从视图获取用户请求并且分派给相应的处理器处理，并决定用哪个视图去把数据呈现给给用户</p><h2 id="DispatcherServlet"><a href="#DispatcherServlet" class="headerlink" title="DispatcherServlet"></a>DispatcherServlet</h2><p>Spring的web模型 - 视图 - 控制器（MVC）框架是围绕着处理所有的HTTP请求和响应的DispatcherServlet的设计。 Spring的Web MVC框架的DispatcherServlet的请求处理流程说明如下图：</p><p><img src="http://www.yiibai.com/uploads/allimg/131224/0J54A451-0.png" alt="img"></p><p>​    </p><p>1.在接收到HTTP请求后，DispatcherServlet通过咨询Handler Mapping来调用相应的Controller控制器。</p><p>2.相对应的Controller控制器接受请求并调用基于使用GET或POST方法相应的服务方法。服务方法将基于定义的业务逻辑设置模型数据，并返回视图名到DispatcherServlet。</p><p>3.DispatcherServlet将需要帮助的ViewResolver从拾取到该请求所定义的视图。</p><p>4.一旦视图被敲定，DispatcherServlet会传递模型数据是在浏览器上最终呈现的视图。</p><h1 id="SpringMVC的实现"><a href="#SpringMVC的实现" class="headerlink" title="SpringMVC的实现"></a>SpringMVC的实现</h1><p>  首先新建一个项目，为它添加Spring开发能力。</p><p>  第二步需要配置web.xml，为其配置DispatcherServlet(前端控制器）和核心配置文件</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">servlet</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">servlet-name</span>&gt;</span>springmvc<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">servlet-name</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">servlet-class</span>&gt;</span>org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">servlet-class</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">init-param</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">param-name</span>&gt;</span>contextConfigLocation<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">param-name</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">param-value</span>&gt;</span>classpath:springmvc-config.xml<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">param-value</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">init-param</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">load-on-startup</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">load-on-startup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">servlet</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>   配置DispatcherServlet其对应的是SpringMVC中的org.springframework.web.servlet.DispatcherServlet类。</p><p>同时指定了SpringMVC核心配置文件的名称和位置（classpath：）。</p><p>   第三步需要实现控制器，下面是我实现的一个检测登录密码是否正确的控制器。</p><figure class="highlight java"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@Controller</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">CheckLoginController</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">@RequestMapping(&quot;/loginController&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">private</span> String <span class="title">handleRequest</span><span class="params">(HttpServletRequest request,HttpServletResponse response,Model model)</span> <span class="keyword">throws</span> Exception </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">request.setCharacterEncoding(<span class="string">&quot;gb2312&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">LoginDao  loginDao=<span class="keyword">new</span> LoginDao();</span><br><span class="line">ShowDao showDao=<span class="keyword">new</span> ShowDao();</span><br><span class="line">List&lt;UserTable&gt; info=showDao.show();</span><br><span class="line">UserTable login=loginDao.checkLogin(request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;id&quot;</span>),request.getParameter(<span class="string">&quot;password&quot;</span>) );</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span>(login!=<span class="keyword">null</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">model.addAttribute(<span class="string">&quot;info&quot;</span>,info);</span><br><span class="line">model.addAttribute(<span class="string">&quot;info111&quot;</span>,<span class="string">&quot;wswp1121&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;success&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;<span class="keyword">else</span> <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;index&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// TODO Auto-generated method stub</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  这里使用的是基于注解的控制器，@Controller是控制器的注解，@RequestMapping注解是用于映射一个请求或者方法。后面的名字是表单中action的值。我的理解是当表单中action的值为@RequestMapping注解的名称，那么就交由该控制器处理。</p><p>第四步是要求配置核心配置文件springmvc-config.xml</p><figure class="highlight xml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?xml version=&quot;1.0&quot; encoding=&quot;UTF-8&quot;?&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">beans</span> <span class="attr">xmlns</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="attr">xmlns:xsi</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="attr">xmlns:context</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.springframework.org/schema/context&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="attr">xsi:schemaLocation</span>=<span class="string">&quot;http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans http://www.springframework.org/schema/beans/spring-beans-4.1.xsd</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag"><span class="string">http://www.springframework.org/schema/context http://www.springframework.org/schema/context/spring-context-4.1.xsd&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">context:component-scan</span> <span class="attr">base-package</span>=<span class="string">&quot;org.controller&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">bean</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;viewResolver&quot;</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;org.springframework.web.servlet.view.InternalResourceViewResolver&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;prefix&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;/&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">property</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;suffix&quot;</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;.jsp&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">property</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">bean</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">beans</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>  其中的prefix以及suffix分别为设置路径前缀和文件名后缀。比如要返回/WEB-INF/jsp/hello.jsp文件是，在prefix的value中只需要写明/WEB-INF/jsp/，suffix只需要写明。jsp，那么返回就可以通过return hello实现。</p><p>  通过以上配置，就完成了SpringMVC的简单配置。</p><h1 id="SpringMVC模式相比于传统MVC模式的优势"><a href="#SpringMVC模式相比于传统MVC模式的优势" class="headerlink" title="SpringMVC模式相比于传统MVC模式的优势"></a>SpringMVC模式相比于传统MVC模式的优势</h1><p>  最后，总结了一些SpringMVC模式相比于传统MVC模式的优势。仅供参考。</p><p> ①拥有强大的灵活性、非侵入性和可配置性。<br> ②提供了DispatcherServlet前端控制器，无须重新开发。<br> ③分工明确。<br> ④可以自动绑定用户的输入，并正确地转换数据类型。<br> ⑤更加灵活的模型数据传输。<br> ⑥内置了常见的校验器。<br> ⑦支持国际化。<br> ⑧支持多种视图技术。如JSP/Velocity/FreeMarker。<br> ⑨提供了一个简单强大的JSP标签库，支持数据绑定功能。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
